PlayerText = \8BSnolf^0
Aim with the camera and use the jump to time your shots' power.

Hold forward to charge vertically first, Hold back to shoot after only charging one direction and hold jump while rolling to brake.

\8BAbility:^0 Mulligan
Hold the Spin button to undo your last shot.

\8BTip:^0 If the camera is getting caught on a wall use the first person view to aim.
